                </ul>
                <p>Elevate your LED routine with full face and neck coverage for consistent all-over results.</p>
            </article>
            <hr />
            <div class="c-bundle-included">
                <p class="c-bundle-included__tile">What’s Included</p>
                <ul class="c-bundle-included__list">
                    <li>
                        <a href="#">
                            <img src="sections/isolated/led-mask-offer/images/q-rejuvalight.webp" alt="Q-Rejuvalight Pro LED Mask" />
                        </a>
                        <div>
                            <a href="#">Q-Rejuvalight Pro LED Mask</a>
                            <small>FDA-cleared device that treats acne, fine lines, wrinkles and dark spots.</small>
                            <div class="e-price">
                                <div class="e-price__main">
                                    <div class="e-price__current">{$dyn}</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#">
                            <img src="sections/isolated/led-mask-offer/images/led-device.webp" alt="Neck & Décolletage LED Device" />
                        </a>
                        <div>
                            <a href="#">Neck &amp; Décolletage LED Device</a>
                            <small>Clinically proven to smooth and firm where aging shows first.</small>
